{"type":null,"faqId":11579,"title":"C8816D  天气时钟","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">在桌面预置的<span>Me Widget</span>（桌面小工具）中已经包含天气时钟，点击小工具，可以打开天气时钟。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">左右滑动可以查看不同城市的天气状态。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">刷新：点击左下角的<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32890\" alt=\"\" />按钮，可以刷新数据。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">城市管理：点击右下角的<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32891\" alt=\"\" />，可以添加删除城市，也可以设置是否显示当前位置。点击右下角<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32892\" alt=\"\" />，进入设置界面，可以设置天气时钟的温度单位和是否显示声音，更新时间等。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32893\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2381","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398502009000,"seriesProductName":"C8816D","visitedTimes":321,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"C8816D","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}